Stop the mistake of stepping on the accelerator pedal!
Four Advanced Supplies - Yahoo! News
you can buy it at a reasonable price.
A traffic accident caused by driver error.
The number of accidents caused by brake and accelerator mistakes by elderly drivers is increasing.
In particular, when it comes to a sudden departure, it becomes a panic, and the accelerator continues to step on the brake pedal.
A new car equipped with a safety driver support function to cover such a driver error is introduced, but there is also a rearing device that can be attached to an unattended car.
After-sales parts manufacturers are developing and selling rapid start prevention and prevention systems.
I would like to introduce what characteristics each has.
The pedal interval between the accelerator and the brake is narrow and the pedal is stepped at the same time.
[e-ACCEL ALARM] "e-ACCEL ALARM" developed by Pivot is to inform you of pedal mistakes from a new perspective.
It is to avoid pedal mistakes with "an alarm sound."
The mechanism generates an alarm sound when you step on the accelerator pedal by mistake of the brake when stopping or driving at low speed.
By reacting to the sound and encouraging the accelerator to return, and by quickly recognizing the mistake of stepping, the acceleration is avoided.
It is difficult to understand changes in engine sound due to the mistake of stepping on the accelerator, and it is also effective for elderly drivers who can be easily heard.
It is attached to the OBDII connector and the main body is attached with double-sided tape.
The price is 9800 yen (excluding tax) and it is affordable, and it is also attractive that you need to set up.
[Ashimo Watching-kun] The World Wing started selling in mid-September with the Ashimo Watch-Do-kun, an accelerator and brake step prevention device.
It is also possible to reverse (back) without moving forward.
At the time of stop (and less than 10Km/h), when the accelerator pedal is stepped rapidly, the vehicle's speed signal and brake signal are detected, and the accelerator opening is electrically suppressed to suppress sudden departure.
When I accidentally stepped on the accelerator pedal, I did not tell the signal from the accelerator and instantly controlled the start by turning it into a creep running state (the brake is removed in the D range).
It also has a function to detect the speed of approximately 5Km/h or more at the time of retreat (back) and force the vehicle to be cleaned.
Installation is possible only with a couplerion and simple wiring processing.
The price is 37,000 yen (excluding tax).
